To save: cx cw
To quite: cx cc

C-v	forward one screen
M-v	backward one screen
C-l	redisplay, positoning cursor at center

C-f	forward one character
C-b	backward one character
M-f	forward one word
M-b	backward one word

C-n	next line
C-p	previous line
C-n	next paragraph
C-p	previous paragraph

C-a	beginning of line
C-e	end of line
M-a	beginning of sentence
M-e	end of sentence

M-<	beginning of file
M->	end of file

C-u n	repeat following command n times

C-g	cancel current command

C-x 2	Open another pane
C-x 1	shink to one pane


<del>	delete previous character
C-d	delete current character
C-k	delete to end of line
M-<del>	delete to beginning of current word
M-d	delete to end of current word
M-k	delete to end of sentence

C-y	yank delete text back

